  "detailed_description": "Under the ghost mountain is a platform shooting Roguelike game.<br><br>Inspire by Spelunky and Downwell<br><br>Gain lifetime by picking apples and killing enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517160/extras/094da01fc06e4054a694948a5654e40f.poster.avif?t=1767109124\" width=768 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517160/extras/094da01fc06e4054a694948a5654e40f.webm?t=1767109124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517160/extras/094da01fc06e4054a694948a5654e40f.mp4?t=1767109124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The lifetime can obtain survival time, and you can also purchase power-ups and unlock levels.<br><br>Bombs can be used to destroy the terrain, or to create the terrain with terrain block.<br><br>Random room, permanent death, Boss bring traditional Roguelike play experience.<br><br>In addition, the chain experience generated by the interaction of enemy death, enemy attack each other, and trap effect on the enemy is also the feature of this game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517160/extras/93e79540ad8870470aaae0d609307f45.poster.avif?t=1767109124\" width=740 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517160/extras/93e79540ad8870470aaae0d609307f45.webm?t=1767109124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517160/extras/93e79540ad8870470aaae0d609307f45.mp4?t=1767109124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Have fun!",
  "about_the_game": "Under the ghost mountain is a platform shooting Roguelike game.<br><br>Inspire by Spelunky and Downwell<br><br>Gain lifetime by picking apples and killing enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517160/extras/094da01fc06e4054a694948a5654e40f.poster.avif?t=1767109124\" width=768 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517160/extras/094da01fc06e4054a694948a5654e40f.webm?t=1767109124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517160/extras/094da01fc06e4054a694948a5654e40f.mp4?t=1767109124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The lifetime can obtain survival time, and you can also purchase power-ups and unlock levels.<br><br>Bombs can be used to destroy the terrain, or to create the terrain with terrain block.<br><br>Random room, permanent death, Boss bring traditional Roguelike play experience.<br><br>In addition, the chain experience generated by the interaction of enemy death, enemy attack each other, and trap effect on the enemy is also the feature of this game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517160/extras/93e79540ad8870470aaae0d609307f45.poster.avif?t=1767109124\" width=740 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517160/extras/93e79540ad8870470aaae0d609307f45.webm?t=1767109124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517160/extras/93e79540ad8870470aaae0d609307f45.mp4?t=1767109124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Have fun!",
